OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775488261
OL,3,CArtemis II approaching far-side of
OL,4,Cmoon never seen before by naked eye
OL,6,FThe Artemis II astronauts are racing
OL,7,Ftoward a new distance record as they
OL,8,Fapproach the moon's far-side - never
OL,9,Fseen before by eye.
OL,11,FApollo 13 currently holds the record
OL,12,Ffor farthest distance travelled by
OL,13,Fhumans from the Earth, but the Orion
OL,14,Fwill go even further than the crew in
OL,15,F1970 on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
