FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775488261
OL,3,CArtemis II approaching far-side of
OL,4,Cmoon never seen before by naked eye
OL,6,FMission Control expect the Artemis II
OL,7,Fcrew - made up of three Americans and
OL,8,Fone Canadian - to surpass Apollo's
OL,9,Frecord 248,655 miles (400,171
OL,10,Fkilometres) from the Earth by more
OL,11,Fthan 4,100 miles (6,600 kilometres).
OL,13,FThe spacecraft will use the same
OL,14,Fmanoeuvre that Apollo 13 did after its
OL,15,Foxygen tank explosion wiped out any
OL,16,Fhope of a moon landing, triggering the
OL,17,Fnow infamous phrase: "Houston, we've
OL,18,Fhad a problem".
OL,26,@yD@VOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
