OL,3,CArtemis II approaching far-side of
OL,4,Cmoon never seen before by naked eye
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FKnown as a free-return lunar
OL,12,Ftrajectory, it is a no-stopping-to-
OL,13,Fland route that takes advantage of the
OL,14,FEarth and moon's gravity, reducing the
OL,15,Fneed for fuel.
OL,17,FIt's a celestial figure-eight that
OL,18,Fwill put the astronauts on course for
OL,19,Fhome, once they emerge from behind the
OL,20,Fmoon Monday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
