OL,3,CArtemis II approaching far-side of
OL,4,Cmoon never seen before by naked eye
OL,6,FIn the early hours of Monday morning
OL,7,FNasa reported that the Artemis II
OL,8,Ftoilet was not functioning again,
OL,9,Fafter it developed a fault shortly
OL,10,Fafter lift off on Wednesday.
OL,12,FThe astronauts were instructed to
OL,13,Fbreak out more of the backup urine
OL,14,Fcollection bags.
OL,16,F"The crew members are able to use the
OL,17,Ftoilet, but we are still trying to
OL,18,Ffigure out the wastewater vent line
OL,19,Fproblem," said Artemis II Entry Flight
OL,20,FDirector Rick Henfling on Sunday.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@IO]
