PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775488261
OL,3,CArtemis II approaching far-side of
OL,4,Cmoon never seen before by naked eye
OL,6,F"When you expose a liquid to vacuum,
OL,7,Fit's a pretty chaotic environment," he
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,FJohn Honeycutt, chair of the mission
OL,11,Fmanagement team, said the astronauts
OL,12,Fwere "trained to manage through the
OL,13,Fsituation".
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
